Package: fin451app
Title: Commodity Futures Risk & Analytics Dashboard
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Student",
           family = "Name",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "student@ualberta.ca")
Description: A Golem-based Shiny dashboard for commodity futures market analysis.
    Covers forward curve dynamics, volatility, co-dynamics, seasonality, and
    hedge ratios across energy markets and fixed income, using RTL continuous
    futures and FRED Constant Maturity Treasuries.
